                <head>No. 478<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On Sunday, February 14, before the seventeenth plenary meeting (see <gloss
                        target="#t_Secto1">Secto</gloss>s 144 and 145, <hi rend="italic">infra</hi>
                    and <ref target="#d480">Document 480</ref>), Secretary <persName
                        corresp="#p_DJF1">Dulles</persName> held a press conference in Berlin to
                    respond to questions concerning the progress of the conference. The United
                    States Delegation transmitted the transcript of the press conference in <gloss
                        target="#t_Secto1">Secto</gloss> 148 from Berlin, February 15. (Conference
                    files, lot 60 D 627, CF 210)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
